:

1. *Voleti* bih da odem na more. (I would like to go to the seaside.)
2. *Volim* da putujem. (I love traveling.)
3. *Volio* bih da čujem tvoja mišljenja. (I would like to hear your opinion.)
4. *Volite* li da učite strane jezike? (Do you like to learn foreign languages?)
5. *Volela* bih da imam više slobodnog vremena. (I would like to have more free time.)